Package component.components.chapter

Class Chapter

java.lang.Object
component.base.BasicStoryComponent
component.components.chapter.Chapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Savable, SavableAsJSONObject<BasicStoryComponent>
public class Chapter
extends BasicStoryComponent
An instance of BasicStoryComponent. A chapter is similar to a marker that can be set to any event card, one chapter per event card.
